body_html:
@petewarden

Thanks for the info. Yes, the problem is that it is choosing to quantize a
Concat node, but can't actually quantize its inputs. I have a fix I will
push out.

This is binary proto before quantization.
tf_mnist_cnn_graph.pb.zip
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/585009/tf_mnist_cnn_graph.pb.zip

Thanks.
